# Testing & evaluation

- Add/update tests for meaningful changes; focus on behavior and failure paths.
- Keep tests deterministic; no reliance on real external providers by default.
- Backend gate (from `backend/`): `uv run ruff check .` · `uv run ruff format --check .` ·
  `uv run pytest`. Frontend: `npm run lint && npm run typecheck && npm run test && npm run build`.
- Evaluation harness (deterministic/mock): `evaluate_agent.py`, `evaluate_rag.py`,
  `evaluate_guardrails.py`. Real-provider evals must be env-guarded and isolated.
- Do not lower coverage of safety, refusal, or approval-gating paths.
